                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The best part about all these dipshits that scream 'nerf' on every other class is that they usually gain nothing themselves.   They just drag down some other classes ability.    Then of course, they also open themselves up to being nerfed since a lot of people have disdain for their pointless whining that got shit nerfed in the first place.
<br />

<br />
    I've known several awesome mages, most of them have quit to move on to other classes.    I remember when all mages did on raids was pump out rods and throw them on the ground -- they've gotten better since those days.  What they don't realize because they are too blinded by their retardation is that enchanters have been getting slowly more pigeon-holed with each expansion and with OoW it has become worse.
