                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">How were mages getting crapped on in this thread?   Several people were 'wowing' at the ignorance of several posters from the Mage Compendium's thread, who were likely mages -- however several people including myself had nothing bad to say about mages in general.
<br />

<br />
    I'm not going to walk on egg shells when it is quite obvious that there are some professional morons, who no doubt perpetuate how great enchanters are and how this was a terrific way to handle charm inblanaces ( READ: GAME DESIGN INBALANCES ), posting in that thread.    There are however a few in the thread who see the changes in the same light as most enchanters do ( READ:  Without the ignorant 'yay we won teh game!' nerf attitude ).
